<p><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在查宿过程中，辅导员们发现越来越多的宿舍变得干净整洁，这是同学们仔细打扫、认真维护的结果，希望继续保持。老师们强调在宿舍须安全用电，严禁使用违规电器，提醒同学们要提高安全防患意识，切不可粗心大意。除此之外，老师们还亲切的与同学们探讨了如何构建和谐的宿舍关系，营造更好的宿舍环境。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmELiclQhpxicHH3ro5n2uiaqWtP9oujeiaYvXOVhDe5qGA50emwZLMlqUCGylbqDzhK6eFGOicbgeftWkMw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="308" height="238" style="width: 308px; height: 238px;"/></span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 25px 15px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 253, 247); transform: translateZ(10px); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">首先我们要做到提高警惕，注意安全。其次睡觉前要把门关好并保持宿舍通风透气爱护公物。最后爱护宿舍楼的一切设施，无消防需要，不得擅自启用消防器材，在查寝过程中这些寝室表现卓越，因此授予星级寝室称号并且颁发流动锦旗和证书，以资鼓励，希望他们继续保持并给其他寝室起到模范带头作用。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section><p><section style="margin: -10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 253, 247); display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; transform: translateZ(5px); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></p><p><br/></p>